text: Charles Ernest Hackett (16 April 1885 – 27 March 1963) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Collingwood in the Victorian Football League (VFL).Holmesby & Main (2014), p.351. == Notes == ==References== * Football: Championship of Australia: Meeting of the "Magpies", The (Adelaide) Register, (Saturday, 15 October 1910), p.11. * Collingwood Football Team: Victorian Champions, 1910, The Referee, (Wednesday, 19 October 1910), p.13. * == External links == * *Charlie Hackett's profile at Collingwood Forever Category:1885 births Category:1963 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players
title: Charlie Hackett (footballer)
